Package: mapcapR
Title: R package for MAPCap data analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Vivek", "Bhardwaj", email = "bhardwaj@ie-freiburg.mpg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: MAPCap (Multiplexed Affinity Purification of Capped RNA) is a CAGE technique that can be performed in a day, and with low input RNA.
            This package can be used for all steps in the analysis of FATSCap data, beginning from read trimming to TSS calling.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.2)
Imports:
    BiocParallel, Biostrings, CAGEr, GenomicRanges, Rsamtools, Rsubread, S4Vectors, plyr
biocViews: CAGE, MAPCap
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
